high_descs: Turn around, walk around the bookshelf, turn to the desk.
Pick the watch up off of the desk.
Put the watch in the bowl on the desk.
Pick up the bowl off of the desk.
Walk back around the bookshelf, walk over between the two beds.
Put the bowl on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Put the watch in the bowl on the nightstand.

high_descs: Turn left to the door, turn right, then right again and go to the end of the desk near the door.
Pick up the watch off of the desk.
Put the watch in the bowl on the desk.
Pick up the bowl and watch from the desk.
Go straight along the desk, turn left and walk past the first bed and go to the bedside table between beds.
Set the bowl and watch on the bedside table.
anns.task_desc: Put away the watch in a bowl on the bedside table.

high_descs: Turn around and then to the right across the room. Turn right again towards the large windows, and look to the desk.
Pick up the watch from the right side of the desk.
Place the watch in a bowl on the left side of the desk.
Pick up the bowl and watch from the desk.
Carry the bowl and turn left to go around the furniture and to the other room. Turn right in between the beds to find the small table.
Place the bowl and watch on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl and watch from the desk to the table.
